Friend should talk to leader of caravan, Popote.
Well, leader in theory, anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041802_MSG0002
rows.name:

Still, dying Nopon deserve nice send-off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041802_MSG0003

Pisa will craft some extra-large Nopon fireworks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041802_MSG0004

Phew! Pisa finally free of Popote...
It been forever since Pisa feel this relaxed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041802_MSG0005
rows.name:
Friend can trust Pisa to handle fireworks.
Caravan will send up biggest, brightest Nopon
fireworks anywhere![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041802_MSG0006
rows.name:
Meh! Pisa not here five minutes before Elder Nan
start groping. Nan keep saying he wants to disappear.
Pisa wish he would hurry up and do it already![ST:wait ]
